          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "If your sons keep my covenant and my testimonies that I shall teach them, their sons also forever shall sit on your throne.” "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 12,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "If your sons keep my covenant and my testimonies that I shall teach them, their sons also forever shall sit on your throne.”"
